Package utilities

Class CustomMapGenerator

  • java.lang.Object
    • utilities.CustomMapGenerator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    public class CustomMapGenerator
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    This class is responsible for loading a map,creating a new map or editing an existing map. This was modified as part of map refactoring to act as single point for map related user interaction.
    See Also:
